  <description>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G0qDnqOKwOE&amp;list=PLJqb_j53o7BiVPaFGQxEHhGx-ximMukwH&amp;index=1

Master BGP in Depth- CIsco Routers
In this video, Sikandar Shaik breaks down the fundamentals of Border Gateway Protocol (BGP)—the backbone of the internet. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced network engineer, this session will help you grasp the essential concepts of BGP, its working principles, and how it manages routing between autonomous systems (AS).
</description>
